    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Construction toys consisting of girders, nuts, bolts, motors and other parts for assembling buildings and structures; first manufactured by the A.C. Gilbert Company in 1913 and later by the Meccano Company.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
